title: Timber winches
summary: A remotely controllable, tractor or forwarder mountable, timber winch

eligible.eligibleBullet02: be either tractor or forwarder mountable
eligible.eligibleBullet05: be controllable remotely using an electric cable or radio control device
eligible.eligibleBullet06: have a pulling force of 65kN or more
eligible.eligibleBullet07: come with at least 9m of wire rope
eligible.eligibleBullet09: have a protection guard to protect driver when seated in tractor cab
